welcome_message_body: "Welcome to National City, the charming and vibrant city known for its rich cultural diversity and delicious cuisine. Get ready to explore and immerse yourself in all that our city has to offer! Enjoy your stay."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at North Island NAS Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at North Island NAS Airport is used exclusively by military personnel and their families.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal for domestic flights and some international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: The secondary terminal for international flights.

wifi.note: Limited free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Brown Field Municipal Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Gillespie Field Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
